Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:02.40,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Hirono.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:06.18,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Is this Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:07.36,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:09.28,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,So I didn't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:13.69,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't disappeared yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:15.23,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.23,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, this is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.69,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:10.94,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,If you read this, you'll be able to find your lost self.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:13.95,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to leave her alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:16.32,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is her own problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:17.31,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:20.68,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to get too involved with Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:25.33,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I should've also told you to prepare yourself if you wanted to stay by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:28.58,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(1473,2140,\1c&H000204&\3c&H000204&\4c&H000204&)}Chihiro has lost four years of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:35.09,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,And even those were just faint images that maintained her original memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:38.49,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,If she spends time reading the diary again and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.57,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,she should be able to return to something like her original state.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:43.39,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:46.06,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that has happened many times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.59,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It will happen again in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:54.18,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,And, the pain will become greater when her memories disappear over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:57.36,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it's even more important that someone stays by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.11,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:01.62,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't talking about Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:04.95,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} will be the one who suffers a greater pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:11.60,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you not to get too involved with Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:12.77,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.00,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.07,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You can still turn back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.47,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment, Chihiro doesn't know about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:23.81,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to disappear from her life, now is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:00.30,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Something doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.06,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Tsutsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:11.10,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, senpai. This is Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.29,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:14.74,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Can you keep me company for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:15.44,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:18.97,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.97,0:04:18.97,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Kioku," which means "Memory."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:27.87,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This is... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.54,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:35.14,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make a difference... whether I read this or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.08,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's always the same day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:42.87,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(\1c&HE8E8E8&\3c&H161616&\4c&H161616&)}I just keep repeating meaningless days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:44.72,bw,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.45,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to keep doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:53.52,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(4250,4450,\1c&HDEDDFA&\3c&H000038&\4c&H000038&)}Do I have to keep doing what's written in this diary from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:56.78,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if I could put an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if I could put an end to such an existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:07.12,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I can't calm down if I don't touch the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:11.50,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you ask Hirono to keep you company?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:15.34,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,His hands are filled with work, so I can't be unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.18,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.13,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.35,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Are you and Hirono getting along well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.08,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,G-Getting along well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:27.99,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-senpai and I are just like siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.89,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,We don't really have that kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:35.77,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, that's why I was asking if you two were getting along well as siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:42.57,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,My mom was an actress when she was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:47.09,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,My mom was really sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:50.18,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make films like those as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.32,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Sparkling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:57.48,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're really sparkling too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.08,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:05:59.86,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:05.34,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,But now, you don't have that sparkle you had when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:09.70,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's because something happened between Hirono and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.73,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I feel like they're getting far away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:18.65,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I noticed, they were in some faraway place I couldn't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:19.65,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.73,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:23.10,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Not just Hirono-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.97,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You're also trying your best at something you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:28.40,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,My younger sister has started writing her novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:32.70,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she's not in a state to do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:36.12,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, I just do nothing because of this injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.39,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sparkling at all like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:42.88,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not the only thing on your mind, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.92,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:53.47,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, right? If I look through the finder, I can see everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.28,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! Long time no see, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:07.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:08.53,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I switched to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.78,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,See? A telephone card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:16.27,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to pay monthly charges, and I don't get weird emails and crank calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:18.01,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It has lots of advantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:20.72,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't be able to call you either, will I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:23.27,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. I might've overlooked that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:30.32,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I stood you up on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.16,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.41,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You're not mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:37.14,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Since you're here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.51,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:43.23,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you were asked to hand in your career interest survey soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:46.51,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep ignoring it, they'll call your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.15,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What will you write?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.74,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'm going to say I want to go to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:53.74,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What about being a manga artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.81,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I write that, they'll call my parents for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:08:01.03,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,In the worst case, they'll find out about my job, and I'll be forced to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:05.17,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad doesn't understand what you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.80,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who got mad and left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:12.48,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that nice, being free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:14.55,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:15.97,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:20.77,bw,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You always seem to walk around all free and at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:21.93,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:26.95,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,My freedom is the empty kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:30.69,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Yours is the freedom to choose what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:36.08,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,A very substantial freedom that you got after
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:38.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,experiencing a lot of hardship and pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.87,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any freedom at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.48,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of things I need to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:46.92,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally boxed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:51.80,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I start thinking about them, they're nothing but headaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:55.51,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If they're a bother, you can just abandon them and run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:09:00.53,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to choose what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:04.02,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're also free to abandon what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:08.61,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. How about running away with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.51,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,To a faraway place that nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.30,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.07,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.34,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're responsible for it since you made the choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:24.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Once I'm involved with something, I can't get myself to run away and pretend it never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.62,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:30.38,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're involved with me too, so you won't run away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:35.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... the truth is, that's the thing I wanted to pretend it didn't happen the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:37.01,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:38.49,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.26,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:45.10,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's someone like you around, I feel like I can let out my excess stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.89,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.49,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:57.03,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I feel really comfortable being with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:01.37,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,But only that little time I can spend with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.02,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.97,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:05.86,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.15,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.15,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.91,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You draw shoujo manga, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:41.87,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any romantic lines for this kind of situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.74,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let go of you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.78,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's really corny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:49.68,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I-I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:50.25,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That's cliché.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:51.75,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Je t'aime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.86,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.35,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you're killed, I will die with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.91,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the wrong situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:00.51,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really a professional...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.49,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good at ad-libbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:11.72,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't have my drawing paper, I can't come up with lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:16.65,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Then take me to a place with drawing paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.71,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about this story?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:24.42,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,They did an experiment before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:25.58,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,An experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:31.58,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of stuff would a baby say if it was brought up without anyone ever talking to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.96,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it would be able to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.94,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Half right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:36.94,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Half?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:42.26,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Not only couldn't it say anything, but it died as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:44.09,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What a sad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:49.03,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,In my case, I didn't die, and I can still talk properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:51.51,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:52.35,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:57.54,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Can you look at me alone at all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:12:00.53,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I will look only at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:05.44,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappear from someone's heart again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.20,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:15.83,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.96,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:21.91,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro has wanted to disappear for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:23.30,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.93,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:30.26,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's natural for you to feel afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:32.10,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's a mean thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:36.12,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why she feels lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:39.64,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Because she's all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.61,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's just the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.10,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Think about the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:46.28,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Then... because she was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.66,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:52.09,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Because she learned about happiness, she feels lonely for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:56.58,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,And because she knows unhappiness, she understands happiness for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:57.75,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:01.03,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,This world revolves around two views on the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:04.09,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, it's about laughable miseries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:04.92,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:09.18,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You two walked into loneliness on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.73,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,No way... There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:14.53,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me there's something else I could do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.19,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied with being able to let it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:21.36,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it comfort you to talk about it to someone?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:26.03,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you keep me away from Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.20,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:30.32,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You should've prevented us from seeing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:34.07,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Maybe I wanted to watch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:39.00,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,A dream that someone like me might be able to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:45.16,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I probably have the answer to what you and Chihiro should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:46.80,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:49.97,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just give you a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:53.84,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Take the story that Chihiro is writing seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:58.72,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Think about the reason she's writing such a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.52,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.52,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Gensou," which means "Illusion."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:06.51,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl started drawing self-portraits the day after the wedding ceremony."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:11.70,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Even though she was married, there was no one except her in her world."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:15.71,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"That's why she put herself into the paintings."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.67,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl put herself into all the paintings."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:23.96,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"In that world beyond, the two of them were laughing together."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:28.72,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Looking at herself in the paintings, she felt strange."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:32.13,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl couldn't really understand that feeling."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:36.22,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Nevertheless, it continued to attract the girl's interest."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.16,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl is only one in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:41.79,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"That made her the God of this world."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.90,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.90,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Odoriji," which means "Iteration Mark."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.40,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Should we take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:51.22,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I baked some cookies. I hope you like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:54.60,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything, Renji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:56.22,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.79,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.12,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Unconsciously, I thought you were older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:03.29,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You can just call me whatever is easier for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:06.29,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, please let me call you what I did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:12.34,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I will go back. I will go back to my former self.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.85,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.85,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Hanpuku," which means "Repetition."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:19.47,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've been writing a novel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.07,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.85,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:26.89,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I need to keep writing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:28.36,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.63,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,We can resume when you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:35.60,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Will you still help me when that time comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.31,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.10,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.10,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Hajimari," which means "Beginning."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:08.69,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've reread it three times now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:13.73,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going back to the person you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:17.50,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You feel just like the usual you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:18.79,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:25.34,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I can love you the way I used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:29.67,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? A-Ah, I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:33.35,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Is it possible you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:39.14,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's more like... you never said you liked me to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:43.47,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I wrote in the diary that I confessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:47.94,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who confessed. Besides, it was like an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.36,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a formal confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:55.24,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Because I wrote that I liked you in the diary many times, I thought I already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.25,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:02.84,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something rash perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.90,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.37,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You could be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:10.63,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget what happened just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.33,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I already heard it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:14.34,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.33,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,For the past four years...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:17.89,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:22.27,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,For the past four yours, I've just been standing still.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:25.36,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should say I was at a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:29.44,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything. There was nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.19,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was just putting up with the passage of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:37.19,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wished I might as well disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:41.95,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It was really painful to read the diary of a person like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:48.58,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But, the diary became really cheerful after I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.19,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Everyday, it was filled with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:54.94,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I felt really lucky just from reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.30,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.62,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,From here to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:01.89,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,These pages are my whole life to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:03.18,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:06.56,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.56,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.56,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Futari," which means "Couple."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.70,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What are memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:14.98,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:19.98,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If memories change, does personality change too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:26.70,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Or does personality stay the same, but the remembered content differs?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:32.36,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... the personality might change if you talk about the exact meaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:36.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but the person herself should stay the same for her whole life in that sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.22,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:40.76,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:44.27,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,When my four years of memories disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:48.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps that former self was already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:59.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also thinking that the former self that spent time with you has already disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:01.36,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.24,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:07.99,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. No matter what happens, you are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:12.25,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't die, nor are you a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:14.00,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:17.92,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Chihiro that I've always known.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.47,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You're a dummy, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:25.04,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:28.08,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:31.44,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm weird, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.30,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:36.15,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's true. It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.15,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.15,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Jijitsu," which means "Truth."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:52.37,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way... no way that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:59.11,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:02.56,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, damn it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:07.56,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro has forgotten about you. Chihiro doesn't remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:10.02,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:14.90,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying Chihiro's existence is more delicate than sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:18.39,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying Chihiro's memories are more fragile than sand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:21.28,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's true. There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:23.03,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro is Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:27.28,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,She met me, she laughed with me. She's been mad, she's cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.78,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Chihiro I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:33.19,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't disappear! She's not a different person!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:36.57,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that... something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:40.87,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.67,Notes Box,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.67,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Yokan," which means "Presentiment."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.98,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.19,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.98,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,There's loneliness here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:01.61,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl is only one in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:04.90,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"That made her the God of this world."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:11.10,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wake Onii-chan up then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.83,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,How about a sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.00,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.59,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.33,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.34,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:29.80,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan, your leg! It's bad for you to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:15.91,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:19.83,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Kei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:21.65,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan! Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:25.88,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:39.49,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Look for me, and bring me back with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:43.68,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, ef - a tale of memories:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.68,0:23:44.68,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:48.18,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have memories you don't want to forget?
